data.description: Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this charming ranch-style home, with its three bedrooms and two baths, embodies the essence of comfortable living. Step into the inviting warmth of the living space, where a cozy fireplace sets the tone for delightful winter nights. The kitchen, adorned with modern stainless steel appliances, seamlessly blends functionality with style, making meal preparation a joy. As you make your way to the back of the home, discover a hidden gem - a screened-in back porch that invites the outdoors in. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or enjoying a relaxing evening while taking in the view of the expansive backyard. Speaking of which, the large backyard becomes an entertainer's paradise, providing the perfect backdrop for gatherings, barbecues, and creating lasting memories with family and friends. Embrace the tranquility and convenience that this ranch-style haven offers, making it not just a house, but a place to call home.
